{
  "stem": "4670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And downstairs, the men were segregated from the women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my grandmother sat in the balcony.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She had the same seat, year after year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she would sit in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She wore this lovely little lace, little kerchief on her head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then we would listen to the congregation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They did not have a choir, but the whole congregation was very fluent in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they would sing and chant together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it was really quite beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I was little, and I had this-- must have had a vivid imagination because of a Rosh Hashanah, the shofar is blown to issue in the new year.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I remembered that I thought it was gold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I discovered later it surely wasn't gold, it's a ram's horn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But I visualized it to be gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I would stand on her seat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She'd let me stand on her seat because I was too little.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You couldn't look over the banister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was an actual banister segregating the upstairs and the downstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I would look down to my Opa, and waited until he would turn around and look at us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "There was no talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that was very important to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to a Jewish school, as I said, the Philanthropin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a secular school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their emphasis was on general education.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was some-- obviously-- some Hebrew that was taught, but I cannot remember any of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know why, but I can't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I am much more-- I was much more involved in the private school that I was in later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the school itself left an important part on my life because the girls that, you know, these were-- the boys and girls were in separate classes.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
